  mso-border-alt:dash-dot-stroked windowtext 3.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;
  height:232.3pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:5.15pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt">《喝饮料》参考解说：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></span></b></p>
      <p class="MsoPlainText" style="text-indent:21.25pt"><span style="font-family:
  仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体">亨瞧，这一家六口，爷爷、奶奶、爸爸、妈妈、男孩儿、女孩儿还有一只可爱的小狗，互相手拉着手，多亲热呀</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312">!</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体">不过，天气也够热的，他们都在出汗。看来，爷爷的扇子也不管用。出了那么多汗，自然会觉得很渴。爷爷说：“走，咱们去喝点儿饮料吧</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312">!</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体">”</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
      <p class="MsoPlainText" style="text-indent:21.25pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      </span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体">桌子上有各种饮料：左边有果汁、健力宝和牛奶；右边有可口可乐、茅台和咖啡；中间还有一壶茶。爷爷喜欢喝酒，抓起茅台就“咕嘟咕嘟”地喝了起来。奶奶还是老习惯，只喝茶，她抱着茶壶大口大口地喝了起来。她认为喝什么也没有茶解渴。爸爸喝咖啡不加糖，不加牛奶。他说喝咖啡就是要喝那个苦味儿。妈妈喝不惯咖啡，她拿了瓶可口可乐，用吸管儿慢慢地吸。男孩儿喝健力宝，说：“喝了健力宝，身体就是好！”。女孩儿不信广告上那一套，她喜欢喝的是甜甜的果汁。小狗只喝牛奶，因为它对别的饮料都不感兴趣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Courier New; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      </span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
  mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:
  1.0pt">“咚……”怎么啦</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:
  仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt">?</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:
  &quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt">有人倒在地上了，大家很吃惊。原来是爷爷喝醉啦</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
  mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt">!</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:
  &quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
